h3.span: Per Governor Murphy, Foundation Academies will remain closed until AT LEAST May 15, continuing to provide online instruction in Google Classroom.

div.p: For complete details, student schedules, meal pickup info for all scholars and more, see our regularly updated COVID-19 page linked below.

h3.b: Según el gobernador Murphy, Foundation Academies permanecerán cerradas hasta AL MENOS el 15 de mayo y continuarán brindando instrucción en línea en Google Classroom.

div.p: Para obtener detalles completos, horarios de los estudiantes, información de recogida del almuerzo para todos los estudiantes y más, vea nuestra página COVID-19 actualizada regularmente en el siguiente enlace.

h2.span: It really does take a village.

p.span: We know that students need a home team support group to partner with our school team, so we will communicate often with parents and welcome your questions and your involvement in your student’s life.

div.p: As a public charter school, Foundation Academies receive about 70% of the per-student dollar allocation that the district schools receive. Our results—100% college acceptance six years in a row––show we get a powerful return on spending.

Can you help bridge the gap by donating? Every contribution helps. To learn how you can significantly support the schools’ initiatives, please contact our Development Office. Phone (609) 920-9200, or e-mail Development@foundationacademies.org. We’ll be happy to discuss our plans with you.
